orm <i>Annes</i> led to some confusion with <i>Ann(e)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Agatha de Brus married Sir Bernard de Brus II before 1264. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died after 1274."},"et":{"–after 1274":"–pärast 1274","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–1329":"1274–1329","–1274":"–1274","1301":"1301","before 1264":"enne 1264","1274":"1274","after 1274":"pärast 1274","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","Exton, Rutland, England":"Exton, Rutland, England"},"fi":{"–after 1274":"–1274 jälkeen","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–1329":"1274–1329","–1274":"–1274","1301":"1301","before 1264":"ennen vuotta 1264","1274":"1274","after 1274":"1274 jälkeen","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","Exton, Rutland, England":"Exton, Rutland, England"},"fr":{"–after 1274":"–après 1274","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–1329":"1274–1329","–1274":"–1274","1301":"1301","before 1264":"avant 1264","1274":"1274","after 1274":"après 1274","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","Exton, Rutland, England":"Exton, Rutland, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Agatha de Brus a épousé Sir Bernard de Brus II avant 1264. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée après 1274."},"de":{"–after 1274":"–nach 1274","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–1329":"1274–1329","–1274":"–1274","1301":"1301","before 1264":"vor 1264","1274":"1274","after 1274":"nach 1274","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","Exton, Rutland, England":"Exton, Rutland, England","lifeSummary":"Agatha de Brus hat vor 1264 Sir Bernard de Brus II geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb nach 1274."},"ht":{"–after 1274":"–after 1274","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–1329":"1274–1329","–1274":"–1274","1301":"1301","before 1264":"before 1264","1274":"1274","after 1274":"after 1274","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","Exton, Rutland, England":"Exton, Rutland, England"},"hu":{"–after 1274":"–1274 után","1250–1301":"1250–1301","1274–